entries.journal_entry_completion_summary: You completed the second officer mission for Ellis Arrison by defeating Mummers.
entries.task00_journal_entry_description: You need to speak with Sgt. Eom Nia, who has assignments for you.
entries.task01_journal_entry_description: Defeat 10 Mummers to show that you have what it takes to be a leader of men.
entries.task02_comm_message_text: Good, now find the medallions the Mummers keep with them. Three ought to do it.
entries.task03_journal_entry_description: The Mummers have been stealing precious metals and forming their own medallions out of them. Bring back 3 of these to prove you're worthy to be an officer.
entries.task04_comm_message_text: Great! Now come back to me for your reward.
entries.task05_journal_entry_description: Sgt. Nia is waiting for you to return so you can be rewarded.
